Package: enhanced-image-cropper-kowalski
Version: 1.0.3.C
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Enhanced Image Cropper Team <dev@example.com>
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-pip, python3-venv, python3-tk
Recommends: python3-opencv-contrib-python, python3-customtkinter
Section: graphics
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/your-username/image-cropper
Description: Professional photo editing suite with advanced cropping tools - Kowalski Edition
 Enhanced Image Cropper is a comprehensive photo editing application that
 transforms the simple cropping functionality into a professional-grade
 editing suite with modern design and advanced capabilities.
 .
 Features include:
 - Modern dark theme interface with CustomTkinter
 - Professional crop templates (Instagram, YouTube, Facebook, Twitter)
 - Advanced image adjustments (brightness, contrast, saturation, sharpness)
 - Professional filters and effects
 - Smart auto-enhancement with CLAHE algorithm
 - Noise reduction and histogram equalization
 - Zoom, pan, and transform operations
 - Batch processing capabilities
 - 20-level undo/redo system
 - Export with quality control
 - Extended file format support (PNG, JPEG, WebP, TIFF, BMP, GIF)
